snippet.title: Cute Pet Hospital Game Walkthrough - Video Tutorial
snippet.description:
Cute Pet Hospital is one more hospital-care based challenge for all boys and girls. Basically, your job is to be the best doctor in the world. Use your mouse to interact. Pick up the patients and bring them to the correct room, but remember that the icons must match.
Play the game at: http://www.horse-games.org/Cute_Pet_Hospital.html
Play the most famous animal games at: http://www.horse-games.org/Animal_Games.php
